 loses.<\/p>\r\n<p>I got to play my first game of this with a career firefighter, actually. We played the introductory rules, which are stripped down and easy to learn. We got the required number of victims out to win (barely), then tried to rescue the maximum, and lost.<\/p>\r\n<p>The advanced rules add elements of specialization to the firefighter you choose to play, and it becomes a much more complex and interesting game. I recommend this one for casual-to-serious board game groups. We had a lot of fun with it.<\/p>\r\n<center>\r\n<a rel=\u0022nofollow\u0022 href=\u0022http:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/B0084M8UEE\/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=1789&creative=9325&creativeASIN=B0084M8UEE&linkCode=as2&tag=erfworld-20&linkId=2WNOHF3KBYVFITCZ\u0022><img border=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022http:\/\/ws-na.amazon-adsystem.com\/widgets\/q?_encoding=UTF8&ASIN=B0084M8UEE&Format=_SL110_&ID=AsinImage&MarketPlace=US&ServiceVersion=20070822&WS=1&tag=erfworld-20\u0022 ><\/a><img src=\u0022http:\/\/ir-na.amazon-adsystem.com\/e\/ir?t=erfworld-20&l=as2&o=1&a=B0084M8UEE\u0022 width=\u00221\u0022 height=\u00221\u0022 border=\u00220\u0022 alt=\u0022\u0022 style=\u0022border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\u0022 \/>\r\n<\/a><br \/>\r\n<a href=http:\/\/forums.erfworld.com\/viewtopic.php?f=24&t=6986>What game should Rob try next?<\/a><\/center><\/div>","guid":44685},{"title":"Erfworld Amazon Affiliate Program","description":"<div><div class=\u0022amazon\u0022>\r\n<center>\r\n<iframe src=\u0022http:\/\/rcm-na.amazon-adsystem.com\/e\/cm?t=erfworld-20&o=1&p=12&l=ur1&category=audible&banner=1KNMQ6Z91A8KDJ552HG2&f=ifr&lc=pf4&linkID=4I2EVNPS2IVMOZIT\u0022 width=\u0022300\u0022 height=\u0022250\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 border=\u00220\u0022 marginwidth=\u00220\u0022 style=\u0022border:none;max-width:800px;max-height:600px;\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022><\/iframe>\r\n<\/center>\r\n<\/div><\/div>","guid":45358},{"title":"Last Book Rob Read","description":"<div><p><a  href=\u0022http:\/\